      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about a specific \"part\" anymore. it's just the whole damn thing. i've tried the therapy, the routine, the meds... everything. but the pattern stays the same. i wake up, i struggle, i fail, i repeat. it feels like i'm just trapped in a loop that wasn't meant to be fixed. there's no \"new angle\" when the system itself is broken.",
